videos.description: Mississippi State's Quinndary Weatherspoon catches a pass in transition and nails the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Weatherspoon knocks down early 3-pointer vs. Cincy

videos.description: Mississippi State's Reggie Perry muscles down an offensive rebound then goes back up to make the layup, adding a free throw attempt on the play.
videos.headline: Perry powers through Cincy defense for and-1

videos.description: Aric Holman gets a steal and pushes it ahead, leading to a one-handed dunk by Tyson Carter.
videos.headline: Mississippi State steal leads to Carter slam

videos.description: Lamar Peters throws a wraparound pass to Reggie Perry, who throws it down over a Cincinnati defender.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Perry puts Cincy defender on poster
